826
00:59:58,174 --> 00:59:59,803
Dia teman pertamanya di sini.

827
00:59:59,874 --> 01:00:01,314
Begitu pun dengannya.

828
01:00:06,214 --> 01:00:07,754
Haruskah kita berteman juga?

829
01:00:09,653 --> 01:00:10,823
Begitukah?

830
01:00:12,484 --> 01:00:14,194
Berhentilah bicara formal.

831
01:00:14,953 --> 01:00:16,694
Bolehkah aku terus
memanggil namamu?

832
01:00:16,694 --> 01:00:17,863
Tentu saja.

833
01:00:18,394 --> 01:00:20,493
Maksudku, ya.

834
01:00:26,703 --> 01:00:30,774
Seperti yang kamu tahu,
